rows.label: qst104502_msg0002
rows.name:
Snififi open shop at Superbian Garrison
that friends can see from here!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0004
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff, sniff-sniff...
Snififi catch smell of strong monsters!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0005
rows.name:
Is Amman Balgas!
Very scary monster!
Probably gobble Snififi up!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0006
rows.name:
If friends defeat three of monster,
Snififi probably able to secure safe
path to destination.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0008
rows.name:
Snififi will watch friends from safe
distance, and make dash for it as
soon as it look safe!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0101
rows.name:
Please defeat three of
Amman Balgas.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0102
rows.name:
At instant of defeat, Snififi and fellow
merchants will dash to destination!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0103
rows.name: We meet up at Superbian Garrison!
